text: Aurora [singing]: Broken me and broken them
Aurora: I've been on this journey, this wonderful journey,
and when I write, I'm reminded of who I really am.
Aurora [singing]: I've been looking for the conqueror.
But you don't seem to come my way.
Aurora: I like seeing myself becoming better
and to try to make the best Aurora song I can ever make.
And that gives me lots of sparks to always try to be more real.
